Class Burrito

  • java.lang.Object
    • Burrito

  • public class Burrito
extends java.lang.Object
    JavaDoc Comments: This is the Burrito class which represents the type of burrito and its contents as well as its cost. This class was created to assist with the BurritoOrder and ChipotleDriver classes.
    See Also:
    BurritoOrder, ChipotleDriver
